---
title: Berbere Lamb Rissoles with Roast Veggie Toss & Garlic Yoghurt
description: These simple low-carb rissoles are packed with moisture and flavour by using rich lamb mince and Berbere seasoning. They’re
the perfect little parcels of joy to be savoured with an easy roast veggie toss and a garlicky yoghurt.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
